c: 22
v: 25
t: "Dhugumatti, isaan kafaranii, karaa Rabbiitiifi masjiida kabajamaa isa namoota ishee (Makkaan) keessa jiraataniifi biyyoota biraa irraa dhufaniif wal qixa goone irraa (namoota) dhorgan, (hoonga’an)Nama ishee keessatti sababa miidhaatiin jallachuu fedhes adabbii laalessaa irraa isa dhandhamsiifna"